SUMMARY:FoodFit for Ukranian Speaking Newcomers: Winter 2026
DESCRIPTION:A 12 week cooking program for people of all ability levels. Focused on building our nutritional literacy and promoting healthy habits\, this program helps balance diets with tasty\, affordable recipes. We increase our physical activity levels by focusing on daily walking as a form of easy and cost-free exercise. \n\n\n\nSession: Winter 2026\, Jan 13 – April 7 Day and time: Tuesdays\, 11 am – 2:00 pm Location: Scadding Court downstairs kitchen
URL:https://scaddingcourt.org/event/foodfit-for-ukranian-speaking-newcomers-winter-2026/2026-03-24/
LOCATION:Scadding Court Community Centre\, 707 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5T2W6\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Community Programs
END:VEVENT
